<br>
The slower weapon swing is Drastic.<br>
<br>
Fully buffed with Aanya's and My Runbanded Girdle my weapon swings with the delay of 33. However when my stamina hits 0 I am swinging the weapon as if I have no Haste at all.<br>
<br>
While this may go relatively Unnoticed on a faster weapon my delay 60 is seriously noticable by everyone in the group.<br>
<br>
It is almost as if once my Stamina bar hits 0 I lose all haste effects.<br>
<br>
